{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And being a yeshiva bocher and being so-- and to, to many times, you know, you had to-- when they opened the, the, the door, when the steel is boiling, and you had to throw in some raw material, by the time you got there, you throw in the shovel with everything, because you couldn't hold onto it.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when you had to rebuild those ovens, they used to send us in while the, the ovens were still boiling hot.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- I don't know if anybody's familiar how does, how the steel is boiled.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the accumulation of the, of, of the, of the stuff, they have to be cleaned once in a while.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was our work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was unhuman, the type of work that you had to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then most of the time, it was this unloading of steel pieces, from wagons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were sometimes heavy metals, which was impossible to, to carry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you had to devise such-- all kinds of things how to make it work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because otherwise, your chances of survival would have been nil, would have been impossible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was hard for, for, this type of life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Besides, you-- you know, it broke your, your mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It broke your spirit.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
